race.comment: BREE CABANG (1) is progressing well and looks close to another win after hitting the frame from Box 4 last run (22.94) at this track. Has won two of five starts from this draw. Can find winning form. MARIONVALE KEV (2) finished well back at this track last time when a 6 length fifth (22.62) but scored three back at this track (22.77). Form here at the trip sound including three wins. Cannot be taken lightly. GREYSYND MERLIN (4) is a capable type and proved too strong last time to win by 3.5 lengths at Healesville in a handy 17.01 beating Cruising Amy. Deserves serious consideration again. HARD COMPASS (8) will be hard to beat with a drop in distance.

runners.name: Broombrae Fritz
